shipeasy/
├── apps/                       # Application directory
│   ├── next-app/              # Next.js application (React, App Router)
│   │   ├── app/               # App router directory
│   │   │   ├── api/          # API routes (thin adapters to core logic)
│   │   │   ├── auth/         # Authentication endpoints with Better-Auth
│   │   │   ├── dashboard/    # User dashboard pages
│   │   │   └── admin/        # Admin interface pages
│   │   ├── components/        # Next-specific React components
│   │   ├── lib/              # Utility functions and configurations
│   │   └── public/           # Static assets
│   ├── nuxt-app/              # Nuxt.js application (Vue)
│   │   ├── components/        # Vue components
│   │   ├── pages/            # Pages directory
│   │   ├── server/           # Server APIs
│   │   │   ├── api/         # API endpoints
│   │   │   ├── auth/        # Auth endpoints
│   │   │   ├── routes/      # Server routes
│   │   │   └── middleware/  # Server middleware
│   │   └── public/          # Static assets
│   ├── tanstack-app/          # TanStack Start application (React, TanStack Router, Vite)
│   │   ├── src/
│   │   │   ├── routes/       # File-based routes ($lang param for i18n)
│   │   │   │   ├── api/     # API routes (server handlers)
│   │   │   │   └── $lang/   # Localized page routes
│   │   │   ├── lib/         # Auth guards, utilities
│   │   │   └── styles/      # CSS and Tailwind styles
